                        the
                        previous types in order to guess it with the fewest attempts possible.</p>
                    <button class="btn btn-light start-button">Start</button>
                </div>
                <div class="country-tips d-flex flex-column align-items-center justify-content-between mt-1">


                </div>
                <div
                    class="game-panel country-panel d-flex flex-column justify-content-start align-items-center d-none mt-5">
                    <form class="row g-3 country-form">
                        <div class="col-auto">
                            <button type="button" title="Surrender" class="btn btn-danger mb-3 button-surrender"><svg
                                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor"
                                    class="bi bi-flag-fill" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
