                              </svg></p> <span class="position-absolute">Continent</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center justify-content-center">
                            <p><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-thermometer-half" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                                <path d="M9.5 12.5a1.5 1.5 0 1 1-2-1.415V6.5a.5.5 0 0 1 1 0v4.585a1.5 1.5 0 0 1 1 1.415"/>
